General.Name: Saxlund Group AB
General.Description: Saxlund Group AB (publ), an environmental technology group, develops, manufactures, and services plants and equipment for the production of environmental-friendly and resource-efficient energy. The company provides push floor dischargers, sliding frame silo dischargers, tube-feeder biomass reclaimers, hydraulic rotor silo dischargers, trailer docking stations, transportable biomass boiler centres, chain conveyors, screw conveyors, and dewatered sludge cake pumping solutions. It serves electricity, heat and power production, wood and forest, water and waste management, process, recycling, mining, and other industries. The company was formerly known as Pilum AB (publ.) and changed its name to Saxlund Group AB (publ) in July 2017. Saxlund Group AB (publ) was founded in 1947 and is headquartered in Nacka, Sweden.
